Name: Standard Pistol
Description: A standard pistol made with common materials, it is simple in structure and easy to operate.

Name: Tokarev
Description: A pistol from a previous era. Crude but hardy, it continues to see service.

Name: Gloomlight
Description: Designed for silent and rapid delivery of firepower, it boasts both quiet operation and high firing rate.

Name: Wolf Fang
Description: Specialized firearm focusing on single-shot performance. Not very accurate, but inflicts incredible damage.

Name: Zero Scale
Description: Connected to Babylonia's support systems, this weapon is equipped with energy management and ballistic guidance capabilities.

Name: Scion
Description: A large-caliber handgun with an extended barrel, capable of inflicting considerable damage at close range. Its user loves the silver-white finish and has also inscribed fine lettering on the body to embody her conviction of eradicating evil with this weapon.

Name: Standard Knife
Description: Forged with standard high-speed steel. Its blade length is 1.0 m.

Name: Combat Knife
Description: A sword with a blade length of 0.8 m, forged from standard high-speed steel. It is sturdier than standard knives, and its slightly shorter design makes it more convenient to carry as a personal defense weapon.

Name: Unbranded Blade
Description: There is no inscription by the maker, but the blade itself is perfectly sharp and deadly.

Name: Unbranded Blade
Description: There is no inscription by the maker, but the blade itself is perfectly sharp and deadly.

Name: Kuji no Sada
Description: A curious katana based on a legendary blade. No longer suited for the modern battlefield.

Name: Lotus Berserker
Description: In addition to a keen edge, the Lotus Berserker is also connected to the M.I.N.D., allowing it to synchronize with the Construct and enabling different types of attacks.

Name: Inverse - Shadow
Description: Inverse is the name of an experimental project that has resulted in the creation of this prototype.

Name: Sirius
Description: Its power as a weapon is nothing to write home about, but it is much sought after for its attractive appearance.

Name: Sakura
Description: A sword with a blade length of 1.0 m, violently forged from a blend of multiple materials. Surprisingly, its structural strength remains uncompromised. For reasons unknown, the blade gradually turns crimson red with every successive slash.

Name: Crimson Birch
Description: The blade is 0.9 meters long and was forged using a composite process with high precision. The color of the blade gradually changes according to the temperature. In extreme cases, dark red icy veins will appear faintly on the blade.

Name: Sariel
Description: A sword with a blade length of 0.9 m, featuring an edge that can expand from a single to a double blade, leaving enemies with twice the wounds. While it causes little damage upon stabbing into an enemy, it extracts their internal vital fluids upon withdrawal, inflicting prolonged torment.

Name: Levitator
Description: A general-purpose wireless remote attack weapon.

Name: Semi-Auto Turret
Description: A semi-automated Levi-Gun capable of executing simple attacks based on the user's will.

Name: Fish Mount
Description: Equipped with state-of-the-art computing capability, it is able to operate freely on the battlefield, delivering devastating firepower. Has been known to get out of control on rare occasions.

Name: Guardian Mount
Description: Equipped with the virtual personality "Aurora", it is a fully-independent, stand-alone weapon platform that is even capable of forming emotional attachment with the user over time.

Name: Type Zero
Description: Prototype levitator. The dated design limits its mobility, but its firepower is nothing to scoff at.

Name: Benediction
Description: Levitator designed for support Constructs, with improved electromagnetic command field performance at the expense of firepower. Bested used in team operations.

Name: Dragon Wind
Description: Exclusive to the White Swan, its performance is every bit worthy of the grandiose name.

Name: Practice Bow
Description: The most common type of composite bow used as standard equipment at archery practice ranges.

Name: Pulley Bow
Description: Pulley-assisted composite bow, with firepower comparable to firearms.

Name: Falcon E-3320
Description: Developed by Kurono Holdings' weapons development arm, it is as unruly as it is powerful, resulting in production being canceled due to the difficulty of finding suitable users.

Name: Ramiel
Description: Named after the fallen angel, its tracking capability ensures a kill regardless of the environment.

Name: Tonitrus
Description: In order to enhance Tonitrus' electrical conductivity, some special materials have been added to it during the production. Coupled with its resistance to electricity and high temperature, it can adapt to nearly all harsh environments on earth.

Name: Astraea
Description: The cutting-edge design used in this longbow enables its string to withstand high-intensity, repeated pulling. During rapid firing, one can even hear faint echoes of the stars in the phantom of its bowstring. Those who struggle from suffering and injustice often call out for hope and justice. If Utopia truly exists, Astraea will be its answer to them.

Name: Chainsaw
Description: A common chainsaw used in the heavy industry.

Name: Noise
Description: Massive chainsaw that runs on gasoline. Its biggest weakness is the effort needed to get it started.

Name: Lightning Spark
Description: The first generation of chainsaw developed specifically as a weapon. Named after the sparks it created during testing.

Name: Inverse - Chimera
Description: Inverse' is the name of an experimental project. This weapon received the moniker 'chimera' due to its integration of the project's results.

Name: Hydro Heat
Description: Hydro Heat is a hydraulic chainsaw with immense power. Its cutting speed gradually increases over time. It also contains a special reagent that heats up the chain, allowing it to reduce targets' Fire Resistance as it slices through them.

Name: Greatsword
Description: An ordinary greatsword with an ordinary name.

Name: Suppressor
Description: Greatsword with long reach and strong defensive capability, typically used in riot suppression.

Name: Dynamo Greatsword
Description: Greatsword with form-change capability. Able to fire shockwaves when its internal energy tank is filled.

Name: Star of Bethlehem
Description: This greatsword resembles a Christmas tree. The Star of Bethlehem is tightly embedded at the tip—even a fierce swing can't shake it off. The blade isn't sharp, but its bulk makes it a deadly weapon.

Name: Big Kamui
Description: Originally given a different name, it was renamed by Kamui after he took a liking to it. It is able to synchronize with the user's M.I.N.D. and increase its power.

Name: Darkness
Description: Modified weapon recovered from a Corrupted Construct. The obsession of its previous owner can be felt just by holding it in one's hand.

Name: Bazooka
Description: A low-cost, simply structured but highly practical Bazooka, ideal for single-person use.

Name: Rifled Gun
Description: Rifling greatly increases the efficiency of delivery.

Name: Magma Pillar
Description: Prototype cannon equipped with an internal reactor. Be careful of overheating.

Name: Firecrackers
Description: Inspired by firecrackers, this Bazooka features a firecracker-shaped component at the rear that can be loaded into the barrel and launched together during an attack. However, after each shot, a short cooldown is required to allow the barrel to dissipate heat.

Name: Berserk Fusion
Description: Said to have been used by insurgents against the Unified Earth government. Many modifications and additions have been added to the total detriment of usability, to the extent that it almost seems grotesque.

Name: Fusion Dragon
Description: High-energy hand cannon that can fire flames like a dragon's breath.

Name: Machete
Description: A common dagger that has nothing to write home about.

Name: Hunter Knife
Description: Well-designed knife that can be handily wielded even by Constructs who are not good at knives.

Name: Stone Heart
Description: The special alloys used make it much heavier than it looks. Very powerful despite its small size.

Name: Yuan Night
Description: A dagger made for the Lantern Festival. The words carved on its blade are to bless its wielder.

Name: Soul Ripper
Description: The ion vibration mode of this dagger can immediately destroy the pierced structure on contact. Only highly skilled Constructs can master this weapon.

Name: Peacemaker
Description: Pressing the button on Peacemaker's hilt can make it vibrate rapidly, greatly enhancing its cutting force. Its blade also contains trace amounts of radioactive material, causing penetrating damage to enemy components during attacks.

Name: Standard Scythe
Description: A common scythe that has functional sharpness.

Name: Bleak Scythe
Description: A modified Standard Scythe, equipped with a handle and a folding mechanism for easier transport.

Name: Faded Color
Description: Though this weapon was forged long ago and the coating of the blade has faded, it still remains as sharp as ever.

Name: Purple Peony
Description: Purple Peony's luminous blade coats enemies in a thick corrosive layer on impact, rapidly wearing down the outer armor of Corrupted. Once it seeps into internal systems, it can even cause momentary short circuits.

Name: St. Elmo
Description: Made of highly conductive alloys, the foldable design makes St. Elmo more portable. When you wave it, you can see streaks of flashing blue and white, which is characteristic of the sharp discharge of the blade.

Name: Galatea
Description: Galatea is created based on a brand new concept in answer to the dissatisfaction with the existing weapons. It's a perfect vessel that reflects the creator's spirit and holds everything inside. It conveys the creator's feelings and composes an epilogue for the enemy.

Name: Photophage
Description: A greatsword that is worn from countless battles. The wielder has wrapped it with bandages as perfunctory fortification.

Name: Glimpse
Description: This greatsword is blunt and unyielding. The deliberately blunt nature of the blade was designed to torture enemies. Consequently, this greatsword is highly demanding on the user's abilities.

Name: Thanatos
Description: The mechanical device at the hilt of this weapon drastically enhances its cutting performance. Its blade generates intense heat capable of melting through various mechanical structures. To support prolonged solo combat, it also includes a simple self-maintenance mechanism—pulling the lever cleans and repairs the blade.

Name: Astray Explorer
Description: The first ever mass-produced Rail Spear for military use. It is equipped with a powerful blast cannon and also has outstanding performance in melee range.

Name: RL-03C Black Spike
Description: A special-purpose railgun for Task Force Constructs. The warhead has a built-in concussion field that can deconstruct armor upon penetration.

Name: Gungnir
Description: This railgun utilizes experimental components to unleash high-energy output as its core design principle. Engineers have nicknamed it "Sharp Lance" for which it is sure to live up to its name.

Name: Virtuous Contract
Description: A pair of white blades kept by samurai of the East.

Name: Virtuous Contract - Mod
Description: A pair of white blades kept by samurai of the East.

Name: Iron Star Type VI
LogName: 4★ Uniframe: Glaive Iron Star Type VI
Description: The blade of this quaint and well-crafted spear sends a chill up people's spines—keeping them away even when it is only placed on a rack.

Name: Guiyun
Description: Forged from glided steel, this blade will eliminates all in its path. Only when there is no more conflict shall it meet its sheath.

Name: Qinghe
Description: The straight edge opens Heaven; the curved blade opens the Earth. The waxy hilt and obsidian body of this blade leave no room for impurities between Heaven and Earth. Only a benevolent leader is befit to wield such a blade.

Name: Armor Break Type IX
Description: These standard gauntlets have been optimized for their melee user's body features. A boost mode is activated for increased striking force once they come into contact with the target physically.

Name: White Qilin
Description: It is a powerful weapon made with a reckless design policy, carrying a power design that should not appear on gauntlets.

Name: Baji
Description: The technical information of this weapon has been lost, and the only way to manufacture it is to use standard industrial blueprints to execute operating instructions with accuracy of micrometer and nanoseconds. Of course, its power makes this all worth it.

Name: Type-4O Lance
Description: The latest YoRHa model.

Name: Type-4O Lance - Mod
Description: The latest YoRHa model.

Name: Cruel Oath
Description: A black blade used by warriors of the East.

Name: Cruel Oath - Mod
Description: A black blade used by warriors of the East.

Name: Genesis
Description: The outdated and rudimentary structure makes Genesis look fragile and weak, but it can still play a role in term of amplification on frames after countless years.

Name: Solar Ring
Description: It's the modified version of the first generation amplifier "Shi", with a reinforced structure and improved energy transmission circuit, resulting in a significant increase in its output.

Name: Ozma
Description: When the amplifier Ozma is used to amplify bionic animals, sufficient computing support must be provided, otherwise it will be hard to perform its real effectiveness , even be involved by its computing consumption, resulting in limited performance of the bionic animal. The amplification covers various aspects of the bionic animal, even the resistance or application of the bionic animal to punishing. Double-edged sword is the best word to describe it.

Name: Bullet Ant
Description: Purchased under the terms outlined in Babylonia military weapon contract SMS-FY-AF-0223. Cosmos Industries products can always be trusted.

Name: FA2D-AP
Description: A mysterious experimental anti-material gun set. Its barrel was forged from special alloys to accommodate unique armor-piercing bullets.

Name: Scale
Description: On one side of the barrel is the feather-light special flechette-shaped rounds. On the other side is an inevitable ending for their target.

Name: Overture
Description: I mark the beginning of everything. All notes and chants come after.

Name: Odette
Description: The shining steel blade drives the tightened string. Elegant, lightweight, yet unstoppable.

Name: Waldmeister
Description: Soft, rhythmic, but carries a great weight of meaning. It is the wind in the forest, the fluttering of wings, and the happiness of victory.

Name: Standard Gunblade
Description: A mass-produced weapon based on Kara Type I Gunblade, achieving a balance between power and cost.

Name: Kara Type I Gunblade
Description: The Gunblade, a weapon left over from the Operation Acadia, has the craftsmanship long been lost. And now, the Babylonia can only make simple maintenance to keep it running normally. Kara Type I gunblade has more excellent research value than application, and provides an excellent data templet for developing other subsequent gunblades in Babylonia.

Name: Apollo
Description: Not all constructs can withstand the chill it constantly emits, and the fit between the gun and the blade reaches a wonderous peak through cold tempering. The energy released from the muzzle is transformed and utilized in the turbine to the extreme, driving the blade to emit a strong resonance.

Name: Collaborator
Description: It is the first generation of Co-Bots researched and manufactured by Kurono Laboratory in the early days. This refined prototype is based the Medic Bot's design. It retains the function of balancing the user's M.I.N.D. to a certain extent, and maximizes its combat power, making it an indispensable prototype for the improvement of the future Co-Bots.

Name: Animus
Description: It's a Co-Bot developed by Asimov using data templates acquired from numerous experiments. Based on the first generation of bots, Animus is able to not only balance the M.I.N.D., but also share it with its users. Whether it is a Co-Bot with multiple battle modes or a high-performance laser beam to supplement to combat power, both can become a natural extension of its user through Animus' special external link. Such intuitive design... it seems like the most beautiful and ingenious weapon.

Name: Snore
Description: It's a Co-Bot with unprecedented computing power and independent tactical analysis. "He" is equipped with the most advanced external link technology, allowing "him" to link to a Construct's M.I.N.D. Only when "he" is used by No. 21, can "his" true potential be unleashed. Like a bullet pierces the enemy's throat on the battlefield, this Co-Bot has the explosive power of a beast trained for the Colosseum. When you see "him" on the battlefield, you wonder if you are looking at a soul born to fight.

Name: Pioneer
Description: A weapon used by some pioneers in the past during the expansion. It has a simple structure yet multiple functions, but the chain isn't easy to master.

Name: Blooming Rose
Description: Nobody knows whether this weapon would spit out deadly bullets or mocking flowers, or the red glow on its blade is a warning or a reminder. This oddly shaped weapon is as mysterious as its user, making it impossible for others to interpret their real intention.

Name: Durendal
Description: Durendal was long lost in the history of the Golden Age. Rumor has it that its blade can pierce through everything, and its crosshair will reveal all hidden foes. The immortal Durendal will fight along its user until their last breath, dedicating absolute loyalty to the person that it protects.

Name: Oriflamme
Description: One of the prototype weapons developed by the Science Council. The reason they decided to design a weapon as garish as a banner spear is not clear. On second thought, this might be why the banner spear has not been mass produced.

Name: Glorious Knight
Description: A modified banner spear with a golden-tailed flag to indicate its superiority to the prototype. Weapon designers have paid extra attention to the design of the flag to make sure it stands out among the other banner spear prototypes.

Name: Phoenix
Description: This banner spear has seen multiple trials and battlefields, but its shape-memory alloy and self-healing structure has kept it pristine and unspoiled as if it is newly forged. The way it stands unwavering has reminded others of a certain legendary, undying Construct. Or perhaps the shape-memory alloy and self-healing structure are just a white lie? Maybe staff members of the Science Council have kept sneaking into the maintenance room every day to replace it with a new one.

Name: Apocalypse
Description: The spinning wheel of light has significantly enhanced the damage-dealing efficiency of the weapon. The design is thus widely used by other scepters later.

Name: Bipolar Star Rift
Description: The plug-in component keeps revolving around the center, with light as bright as that of the polar star radiating through the gaps.

Name: Hestia
Description: A scepter with a simple coloring scheme and structure, yet an extraordinary amount of energy. There are few records on the scepter, but any description would be redundant. You will understand this the moment you see it.

Name: Standard Mode
Description: I'm the base of rhythms in music. Everything's change is by your ears.

Name: Neapolitan Solo
Description: The black flute looks deep and composed, concealing all the innocence in her heart. Now her charms are all overthrown, she wields the sword to stay committed to her last duty.

Name: Sarastro
Description: A snow-white flute with golden sparkles resembling the light of the sun rising at the end of winter and symbolizing the return of spring.

Name: Gray Iron
Description: A product of the latest technology. It has excellent performance but weighs way heavier than a standard weapon.

Name: Whitefrost Ruler
Description: A weapon with an unconventional straight blade design. In order to increase its overall stability, the designer has added extra metal rivets to the blade.

Name: Infinity
Description: A weapon designed by a dancer. Maybe that's why it looks like a prop for performance.

Name: Rage
Description: A mass-produced saw component made with standard alloy. Cheap, big, and economical.

Name: Red Shift
Description: The modified chain component has an upward-pointing blade top and enhanced sawblade, making the saw even thicker. The personalized coating has been improved at the user's urging, as "making it cool" is the ultimate goal.

Name: Implosion
Description: The latest mega saw plan designed by Nanami. It features a complex joint structure and a conspicuous coating. Powered by the Energy Core's sudden increase of temperature, the sawblade will reach its max explosive power.

Name: Blast Hammer Prototype
Description: A strange weapon modified from engineering equipment primarily used to explore new methods in weapon development. Long-ranged firepower has been added to make up for its lack of power at close range.

Name: Despair Breaker
Description: By integrating the data collected from its prototype and the feedback from the prototype's wielder, it has eventually become an even more powerful weapon than its original model. The grip, power, trajectory, and a hundred other improvements have all been made, resulting in a weapon capable of shattering any doubts and despair.

Name: Illuminare
Description: The creation of Illuminare is a game changer in Babylonia's weapon development history: its performance-centered exterior is revolutionary, it is committed to maximizing destructive power, and even its wielder, Karenina stormed into the Weapons Design Bureau pressing for the removal of safety limiters. There is no doubt that its final result will be exactly what Karenina said, "This is gonna send all the enemies out of this galaxy!"

Name: Hope of the Village
LogName: 4★ Rev Blade Hope of the Village
Description: The weapon given to the adventurer before they set off usually carries the hope of the entire village. Don't you think this is a perfect name? You'll feel full of courage just at the thought of fighting for the village.

Name: Progressive Knife
Description: Babylonia has improved the performance issues of the old blueprint and remade the Rev Blade with strong materials. "Progressive Knife" is a name Noan came up with himself. It seems he got the inspiration from a manga he read. "Great name. Promise me don't name any weapon next time." —Weapon Designer H

Name: Prometheus
Description: A Rev Blade made with the improved blueprint by Babylonia's weapon design department. It uses upgraded materials and perfectly matches the off-hand old sword. However, it is restricted by the old design after the overall improvement of performance and requires regular maintenance. What Noan does is hit it several times.

Name: Dusk Mirage
Description: An extensible sword that makes its owner able to fight flexibly. Its low-key gray color might not stand out, but the energy hidden in it is astonishing.

Name: Polar Night
Description: The sword's blade and body have been converted to match the latest specialized frame with its coating changed to a more transparent black color. The world will be launched into an eternal polar night when the power in the sword is released through its blade.

Name: Hecate
Description: One of Kurono Tech's best products. A perfect combination of elegance and wildness. When the executor wields the sword as if she is making a prayer, it looks like the multi-faced goddess of the crossroads in the myth has descended to bring victory to her allies and the end to her enemies.

Name: Heartless Blades
Description: A sword doesn't have a heart. It only needs to be wielded by its wielder... Is it not?

Name: Comet's Edge
Description: A composite weapon with a transformation blade. Created by adopting the newest molecular dynamics technology, its silver blade has a much more lethal curvature and emits a faint blue glow.

Name: Sound of Silence
Description: A new-generation special-grade weapon created by Babylonia. While its weight has been further reduced, the argon gas vacuum condensation technology has brought the durability and sharpness of its blade to a level that ordinary metals are impossible to achieve. Repeated hammering and heating also cause its blade to emit a dark blue glow. When wielded, its wielder seems to be controlled by invisible strings to deliver silent death.

Name: Composite Armaments Prototype
Description: This prototype of Composite Armaments can satisfy the user's needs in close, medium and long range firepower based on the battle situation. The materials used in the relatively more fragile transforming mechanism have all been electro-magnetic processed to ensure a reliable and smooth transition between different forms.

Name: Nuclear Meltdown δ
Description: This set of Composite Armaments has been specially approved by Babylonia's Military Weapon Development Center to use an experimental δ-ray core as its energy supply. This is the first time a δ-ray of this scale is deployed on a weapon, so its user must have the ability to master the pace between the δ core's energy output and instant cooldown.

Name: Key of Tempus Gate - Stokes
LogName: 6★ Composite Armaments - Key of Tempus Gate - Stokes
Description: Mankind needs a hope that can confront this dark era. Cosmos Industries, Weapon Development Center and the user Lee himself have discussed many times to calibrate his specialized frame and its exclusive equipment. After installing an additional tactical AI, this weapon has been pushed to its limit in all aspects. "There's no need to compromise to the environment; I won't allow any mistake to happen."

Name: Paintbrush Prototype
Description: It was originally designed to be a multipurpose painting tool, but after a range of features were added for convenience's sake, it achieved an unexpectedly high score in the Science Council's weapon testing session.

Name: Dual Rainbows
Description: To accommodate the WGAA's newest frame's specifications, this Beam Gunlance has been modified for the finest adjustments on each parameter. As strongly required by Ayla, it also retains a painting function, which makes it one of Ayla's favorite paintbrushes.

Name: Star Voyager
Description: A Beam Gunlance made exclusively for Ayla after undergoing a meticulous final adjustment. It is, in fact, her dream weapon as it absorbs different suggestions and inspirations from many Constructs, which means it is a work involving all her friends.

Name: Swiftplume
Description: A custom weapon made of an odachi and a kodachi. It merges a nimble style with beast-like sharpness.

Name: Red Sprite
Description: Infused with the power of Ascension-Network, this legendary blade has the power to cleave through thunder. It strikes like red lightning, obliterating all enemies in its path.

Name: Nightblaze
Description: Forged from an unknown material, this daisho is meant for sole wielders. When drawn, the stored energy gets unleashed, piercing the darkness like the first light of dawn.

Name: Severed Rain
Description: Modified with the technologies of Church of Machina, this fan still possesses the essence of Kowloong with golden threads and santalwood bones.

Name: Returning Wind
Description: Special decorations were added to this fan according to the user's needs, making it look more like a dance prop than a weapon. The fan gives a radiant brilliance when waved, but its power should never be underestimated on the battlefield.

Name: Perpetuity
Description: The special metal used to forge its blades allows it to not only inflict cuts that are deadlier than originally expected on its enemies but also to radiate dazzling light when wielded. After the design draft was completed, Pulao secretly added a flower to the fan's main rib.

Name: Lightning Devourer
Description: The design of these edged weapons is based on the claws of predatory animals. Very few Constructs can adapt to using them in battle as they significantly deviate from the typical human battle mindset.

Name: Trio-Claws
Description: These blades are designed exclusively for No. 21's wild, untamed combat style. The three reinforced energy claws can easily tear through any obstacles.

Name: Managarm
Description: When swung, these Claw Blades would make a sharp, piercing howl as if there is a ferocious beast inside. The blades reflect a chilling light, resembling a lone wolf sharpening its claws in the shattered moonlight.

Name: Golden Heart
Description: Forged from a special alloy, this robotic arm's supersolid layer assembly allows it to withstand high temperatures and pressures. It is a perfect answer to those who question the performance of Construct weapons.

Name: FPT-II - Mod
Description: This robotic arm has adopted a red and black color scheme with a streamlined frame. As requested by its user, additional vents and rectifier have been added to maximize its performance.

Name: Crimson Howl
Description: As the ultimate fusion of engineering and violence, this weapon is Noctis' favorite. The fermions that flow inside the arm are creating non-stop annihilation on a micro level. Even when it is stationary, the roaring noise deep inside the crimson core still longs for explosion and destruction. Noctis himself does not care about any of those features—he is happy as long as the weapon is powerful enough.

Name: Atoll
Description: Inspired by coastal reefs, this weapon's irregular blade makes its attacks unpredictable. Very few can handle this weapon well.

Name: Reversal Node
Description: Amidst dark clouds and storm, the weapon cuts through the rain to reveal its true look. The silver-coated blade may appear to be slim, but no one would doubt its elegance and lethality.

Name: Metis
Description: Back in Atlantis, Lamia read some books that mentioned the weapon used by the God of the Seas—a trident. Those who possess this trident will have the power to rule the sea, and can even bring the dead in the sea back to life. But legends are just legends after all; Lamia only picked up a broken weapon from the sea and modified it into the current form with the power of Punishing.

Name: Rock Cannon
Description: Capable of firing 20 rocks per second, it can also transform into a giant blade.

Name: ★Rock Cannon
Description: With a rock-like appearance and structure, its origins are just as mysterious as its owner.

Name: Black Raven
Description: The new military composite metal has proved it once again that with the enough toughness and strength, it is okay to reduce the weight of a weapon to the minimum.

Name: Pale Plume
Description: The new unimolecule vibrating blade has greatly enhanced the weapon's combat efficiency but reduced some of its stability. In other words, the wielder needs to have a tighter grip. As one of the design highlights, the ergonomic redesign of the handle offsets the defect by reducing the unwanted vibrations when the weapon is wielded to the minimum.

Name: Dark Falcon
Description: What is the best way to get the max killing power while staying suitable for all kinds of battle environments? Having the user carry four or five different weapons? Of course no. You just have to make them into one. This is the unprecedented multifunctional polymorphic design that comes with an expensive price and a complex use logic. No way to be mass-produced. Only designed for the strong.

Name: Emerald Quill
Description: Forged from a new type of alloy, this mass-produced longsword is based on a blueprint and features a sharp blade and a slender body. Its color scheme mainly consists of black and dark green.

Name: Phoenix Edge
Description: This weapon is designed specifically for a monarch, featuring an exquisitely luxurious appearance with intricate patterns carved into the blade, and a deliberately crafted structure that perfectly balances flexibility and cutting power.

Name: Akasha Keyblade
Description: With a golden blade and a jade structure, this sword was crafted and perfected by three masters and has incorporated all the essence of their craftsmanship. Its advanced mechanism allows it to switch between different forms, making it swift, powerful, and lethal. Not only it is a weapon fit for a sovereign, but it also serves as the key to Tabula Akasha.

Name: PESW-II - Mod
Description: A military headphones prototype installed with the Second-Generation Communication Protocol Framework, it excels at high-speed computing and cyberspace conflicts. With its dependable battery life, it can adapts to different battlefields.

Name: White Night's Noise
Description: A portable computer installed with the Third-Generation Communication Protocol Framework, it performs as a tactical terminal during cyberspace conflicts while possessing a high-grade firewall. On top of that, it is also a working headphone as it appears to be. With military-grade modules, it is capable of audio analysis and monitoring environmental information in real time. It may be small, but it is mighty.

Name: Hacker's Tune
Description: With an amplifier disruptor and a miniature active radar, this weapon can detect and track nearby targets while recording suspicious signals. High-speed channels and mimic firewalls grant this weapon high offensive and defensive power, ensuring the efficiency of cyberspace battles while reducing the inaccuracy of close-range information. However one puts it, this weapon is a far cry from its intention and its adorable appearance.

Name: Reappearance
Description: Condensed from the Red Tide, this weapon embodies a new power that has transcended countless hardships. Though its form is still somewhat naive, it already radiates a brilliance sharp enough to shake the world.

Name: Dark Moon
Description: Withered plants must be burned down before new trees can grow. Only absolute destruction can lay the path to true rebirth. No one can halt the incoming revolution—she never fears the cost of change.

Name: Reconstruction of Law
Description: No law or theory can bind this weapon, for it has the power to reshape all the principles that the world runs on. It tears apart everything it sees, reconstructs them, and crushes them again like a child whimsically playing with building blocks.

Name: Standard Tactical Tonfas
Description: Developed specifically for the Support Force, this mass-produced weapon features superb stability, a simple and intuitive design, and a user-friendly structure, making it suitable for most rescue missions.

Name: Everburning Ray
Description: This specialized weapon is a second iteration developed from the successful Standard Tactical Tonfas. The built-in Energy Shield has undergone thousands of stress tests to ensure it can save the user's life in any extreme environment.

Name: Cestus
Description: After receiving ample funding, Babylonia's weapon research department has developed this masterpiece with confidence. Crafted with an arsenal of cutting-edge technologies, this weapon is engineered to withstand immense pressure under any circumstance while delivering brutal, destructive power capable of pulverizing any enemy bold enough to stand in its way.

Name: Frontier Foliage
Description: As the famous Kowloong lyric poem Song of Concubine Ming goes, 'She travels thousands of miles on horseback with her pipa, the spring back in the palace now feels like a whole different world to her.' After the strings are broken and buried in sand, summer arrives, but there would be no one to appreciate the beautiful scenery.

Name: Moonside Petal
Description: Arriving like spring, a bird that lands on a branch, she plucks the strings in the moonlight under the begonias and performs Faerie Melisma. The melody flies up and reaches the heavens in the tranquil night.

Name: Dream Roamer
Description: Is it real or is it all but a dream? When the music starts, the butterfly dances, and a dream will be created. Leave the question aside until the song is finished.

Name: Load & Rest
Description: It was specifically stated that it should not have an overly complicated design because it would be hard to carry around. Most importantly, that will affect Wanshi's ability to sleep on the spot when he wants to.

Name: Eternal Peace
Description: Upholding the rule of "a clear view is essential to a clean hit", it has precision on par with a sniper rifle. The user had other expectations for it, hoping that it could be like a certain mythical item from the legends, to not only protect the living, but to also escort the souls of the deceased on the path to eternal life.

Name: Renewed Dawn
Description: After numerous tests to guarantee projectile speed and enhance the support function of the drone as per Wanshi's suggestion, it can now perform rapid shooting without losing firepower or precision. When asked for the reason for these modifications, he replied that he did not want to be in a situation where he lost either speed or power again and leave more regrets.

Name: LB - Flash Prototype
Description: A prototype weapon made according to the latest military directives. It features a blade stem embedded with a pyro core and an exterior forged from high-entropy alloy, capable of slicing through steel like butter. Originally designed to test the limits of the pyro technology, its remarkable performance has led to its formal induction into active duty.

Name: Mist Netherlight
Description: Through endless struggles of life and death, the girl etched every skill learned in battle in her heart. With every strike of her blade, the echoes of the past reminded her: her fight was far from over, for those still fighting, and for those who could fight no more.

Name: Flamewing of Dawn
Description: Ashes rise in gray flames, the golden rays dispel the gloom. No matter how dark the abyss, the fire of the red lotus will bloom with the brilliance of dawn. No matter the obstacles ahead, the girl will soar on wings of hope, triumphant as promised.

Name: Rasetsu
Description: This new weapon, forged from military-grade prosthetics using a revolutionary super-solid layering process, excels in diverse combat scenarios and significantly boosts individual combat effectiveness. Its potential is immense, whether deployed on the battlefield or adapted for civilian use.

Name: Raijin
Description: Legend speaks of a night in antiquity, wind howling, clouds obscuring the moon, and demons prowling. Suddenly, a thunderous roar shattered the gloom. A deity, cloaked and staff in hand, descended upon a bolt of lightning. In a blinding flash, the demons scattered like chaff before a storm. This was the Thunderous Exorcism, a tale whispered through the ages. —From the "Garden of Wonders"

Name: Fudo Myo-o
Description: A lone traveler, burdened by the weight of time, trudges along a frozen path, adrift like a single leaf on a vast ocean, finally reaching the end of the labyrinth. A thousand years have passed, yet the air still hums with the scent of flowers. The world shimmers with illusions, a kaleidoscope of reality and fantasy. This time, she seizes the fleeting moment, unleashing a torrent of thunder, shattering the illusions.

Name: Shield Axe ZL-07 Prototype
Description: Crafted from standard alloy, this Shield Axe is both offensive and defensive, capable of multiple form transformations. But due to its weight, mass production was not approved.

Name: Sparkle ZL-09 - Mod
Description: Its platinum color and the radiance it emits during battle are reminiscent of the glorious colors in Golden Age mecha anime. Take up "Sheen" on the battlefield and blaze a new trail that still shines bright.

Name: Starlight Glare
Description: Perfectly recreating the legendary divine weapon from the girl's wild imagination, every part can be extended into a dazzling combo. Its goal is to cut through all boring things, like loneliness and sadness. Even "unchangeable" fate will be shattered by it.

Name: The Last Answer
Description: Designed to traverse unknown realms, the prototype of this key-shaped probe boasted nearly unmatchable computing power for unobservable universe exploration.

Name: Celestial Reflection
Description: Amid an ever-expanding cosmos, in domains beyond light's grasp, this "key" holds an incalculable trove of data that mirrors all the death and rebirth throughout the universe.

Name: Alpha-Omega
Description: With a power unpredictable as fate itself, this scepter bends the boundaries of creation and destruction beyond the measures of space and time.

Name: Rosy Silhouette
Description: The appearance is inspired by the hand umbrella knife of the female lead in some famous Golden Age crime movies. This design has some practical value, but it can only lie in the collector's showcase due to its heavy handle.

Name: Glazed Enigma
Description: Compared to its predecessor, this one is a true "weapon" with the handle made of a low-density material. The umbrella fabric has been replaced by a low-key translucent white color to indicate the production process upgrade.

Name: Sorrow of Fata Morgana
LogName: 6★ Moon Umbrella  Sorrow of Fata Morgana
Description: A weapon reconstructed with the help of the Ascension-Network after Lilith passed the trial. The luxury platinum patterns and the highly concentrated Punishing Virus clad layer on them have made it an elegant but fierce killer weapon.

Name: Verse Abiding
Description: A prototype Bowstring Rapier designed by the Science Council with a pressing device that has features of an entry-level musical instrument. When the strings are bowed, it would create an ethereal resonance on the battlefield.

Name: Crowned Laurel
Description: An improved Bowstring Rapier crafted by the Science Council with enhanced concert feature that makes the pressing device a "baton." Whenever a light shoots across the sky above the Bowstring Rapier, the pressing device will create a harmony as grand as a symphony orchestra in performance following the user's order.

Name: Orpheus' Lullaby
Description: A weapon co-created by the WGAA and the Science Council with "crafted for those who devote their lives to art" as the concept. However, it has no difference from common music instruments in terms of craftsmanship and design. The only decisive difference is that it uses precious inert metals that make it sound just as clear as today even after hundreds or thoudands of years.

Name: Standard MK II
Description: Designed and manufactured by Leibowitz Company, this general-purpose Fusion Gunsword is widely issued to armed personnel.

Name: Lethal Shadow
Description: A "weapon of war" for the humanoid weapon of war. A weapon wielding another weapon—what, then, is the true difference between the two? —Weapon Designer L

Name: Final Arbiter
Description: Generated by the Matrix's computing power, even when operating at under 10% of its total output in daily use, it possesses terrifying destructive capability. No enemy has ever lived to see it at full charge—because in the very next instant after its energy port begins to glow, they are already dead.

Name: Firecrash
Description: The designer drew inspiration from Golden Age legends of valkyries and created this rare weapon that combines the elegant appearance and extreme kinetic energy. It can adapt to all kinds of battlefields and swiftly switch between a spear and dual blades, meeting the user's demands for both melee and ranged battles.

Name: Fiery Twilight
Description: As required by the user, the designer has greatly optimized the weapon's charging module and further adjusted the weight ratio of the grip part to the attack part.

Name: Deathless Flame
Description: An excellent weapon with further improved coating and charging module based on the battlefield statistics collected from previous battles with more funding from relevant departments. The designer opened a full sugar ice coke with relief on the day the weapon finished its final adjustment.

Name: Yamato - Kageuchi
Description: A legendary sword that looks similar to Yamato. It can't separate things like Yamato but can surely slice an enemy in half.

Name: Yamato
Description: A powerful sword capable of separating the human and demon halves of an individual. Rumor has it that the sword was left by Vergil's father as a keepsake and is also the source of his power.

Name: Devil Hunter Sword
Description: This replica of Devil Sword Dante looks very similar to the original but is able to enhance the power of fire due to the demonic materials added during forging.

Name: Devil Sword Dante
Description: It's not yet clear whether Dante merged the weapons with his own power or Rebellion did it itself, but this Devil Sword is a new weapon regardless.

Name: Smiter
Description: This weapon, with its transformable blade, boasts exceptional performance. Don't let its general-purpose, mass-produced status fool you; its power is nothing to scoff at.

Name: Night Sunderer
Description: Each part of the transformed blade can operate as its own combat unit. The tougher the fight, the more thoroughly its incredible potential shines through.

Name: Aurora
Description: This weapon is sleek, slender, and elegant in form, yet deadly, dangerous, and overwhelmingly powerful—a perfect blend of beauty and lethality. When Bianca first takes hold of it, the radiant glow from its core looks just like the first light of dawn breaking on the horizon.

Name: Laceration
Description: At Discord's request, the design remains simple and undecorated. The familiar shape reminds her of the ordinary scissors she once used, the soft and gentle texture of fabric still lingering at her fingertips—she still remembers that quiet dream of sewing and cutting.

Name: Spinebreaker
Description: Throughout development, fluidity was prioritized, and optimization was carried out to achieve the excellent results seen today.

Name: Osseous Guillotine
Description: The designer is most satisfied with the color scheme, which is a little unconventional. "Simple, efficient and sharp! That's what makes a design perfect. There's nothing wrong with being different—only by not caring about others' opinions can you stay true to yourself."

Name: Flamethorn
Description: The lances used in tournaments may look magnificent, but they are actually constructed with hollow cores, similar to those wielded by winged hussars. This design ensures a solid feel while maintaining excellent balance and weight distribution.

Name: Skyradiance
Description: Based on its performance, the weight and energy conductivity have been significantly modified. While a skilled wielder can find their balance, the lance's sheer heft is an inescapable burden. True mastery of this weapon demands extensive real-world experience.

Name: Empyrean Wrath
Description: Tempered through countless fierce battles, this ultimate lance enables a mighty leap. At its apex, the lance shifts its stance, allowing the wielder to channel the full weight into a devastating plunging attack.

Name: Lotus Wheel MW-03 Prototype
Description: Built from Liv's new frame, the Empyrea frame's scepter was turned into a floating core, and controllable blades were added around it. The Engineering Force named this prototype weapon the Spinning Blade.

Name: Cyan Blossom
Description: This perfected Spinning Blade system strengthens the link between the core and its wielder. Its blades are now lighter than ever, allowing smoother transitions between long-range attacks and close- to mid-range slashes.

Name: Ripples of the Aloft Sea
LogName: 6★ Lotus Wheel Wheel: Ripples of the Aloft Sea
Description: A lotus in the air, an ocean within the lotus, and ripples upon the sea... Countless thoughts break and drift within the deep water mirror, gathered in a girl's palms as she guides them into a gentle dance.

Name: Weapon Enhancer
Description: An Omniframe weapon exclusive enhancement set. It can bring different levels of enhancement to a weapon based on its size.
